Project Scope
Make an app that shows all the available options for Men, women and kids dresses. User should be able to download the app, search his favorite dress, add to cart, pay and purchase.

In scope- Make an app that enhances the sales of TF and eases customers search on the app, give lots of options. Easy to navigate, search and make a purchase. Getting email and message updates about the order, shipping details and confirmations at all stages. 

Out of scope- We do not provide a web version of the app. No international purchases or payments. Doesn't include multiple payment methods.

Objectives and Deliverables
For the ease of shopping at home, to know what all a customer can get in TF, a TF Store application is to be made, that lets the user browse the dress options at TF and purchase from the TF Store application itself and hence their product should be delivered to the door.

Business Goals:
The TF app should be ready within the next 5 months under $50k budget.
An app that offers customers a wide variety of options for their personal, family, seasonal or quick shopping.
A fast and easy navigation for customers to explore their options at TF Store (app).
An app that priorities user's data safety, safe payments and correct, timely order placements
Aim to engage customers in the app by 40 to 50 mins per week
10% of website visitors should be purchasing via the app.
In the competition of existing online shopping apps, TF Store (app) should record download of 50k in the 1st month, 60k in the 2nd month and so on. By the end of 6 months aim for 5L downloads and 2L customer profiles to no created.

